@node notes "Scribbled at the end..."
                               NOTES
                               -----

Some notes on this guide:

I did not include documentation in the .doc format, since @{U}everyone that
has AmigaDOS 2.04 and up should have AmigaGuide@{UU}. Besides, the structure of
this document would make translation quite hard. If you happen not to have
AmigaGuide, and are pissed off by the weird format of this document, I
suggest you get AGuide package from AmiNet - it's even better than
AmigaGuide!

For the Polish users:

I did not include the documentation in Polish, since @{U}I believe that
everyone that uses public domain files should know English! (everyone that
uses a computer should!)@{UU}. So treat this as an exercise.
@endnode

